02-12 18:49:00','I think there could be two different approaches to innovation: \nthe first one aims to capitalize tech innovation and to grow fast intersecting technology and finance without considering any social externalities.  Schumpeter.. you know, and this vision brought us at this point.\nThere\'s another approach that considers that this world, or better the human kind (the planet is actually going quite good) is living a very important moment in its history, you know.. there\'s a new tech revolution, but also global crisis, climate change, Syria destroyed, Paris attack, israel/palestine still in 2016, more plastic than fishes in the oceans.. and so on. So, said that, I think could be useful to think, to discuss, to understand, before to do anything that could change drastically our finance and governance, because, dear Alex, we should stress that people, that study economy, philosophy, law, politics, sociology and whatever, are not only morons that weren\'t clever enough to become engineers.',0,'1','Disqus/1.1(2.84):2510344249','',19,0),(44,120,'Décentralisation du travail et blockchain &#8211; Blockchain France','','http://blockchainfrance.net/2016/02/13/decentralisation-du-travail-et-blockchain/','192.0.101.193','2016-02-13 15:21:46','2016-02-13 15:21:46','[&#8230;] cours du temps (equity – commodité – monnaie). Pour plus d’informations, vous pouvez visiter ce lien (en [&#8230;]',0,'1','The Incutio XML-RPC PHP Library','pingback',0,0),(45,332,'Bitcoin, Blockchain et politique : ne pas se tromper de disruption - Le Coin Coin','','https://le-coin-coin.fr/3593-bitcoin-blockchain-politique-ne-se-tromper-de-disruption/','217.70.186.133','2016-02-16 12:43:34','2016-02-16 12:43:34','[&#8230;] du magazine en ligne de Backfeed le révèle cependant très vite. Je suggère la lecture de la débâcle du bitcoin pour se forger une [&#8230;]',0,'1','The Incutio XML-RPC PHP Library -- WordPress/4.4.2','pingback',0,0),(46,120,'Jake Bedard','jacob.bedard@gmail.com','','73.250.